headline: Carrier First Quarter 2025 Earnings Advisory
summary: Carrier Global Corporation (NYSE: CARR), global leader in intelligent climate and energy solutions, will release its first quarter 2025 earnings on Thursday, May 1, 2025 and host a conference call and webcast at 7:30 a.m. ET.

headline: Carrier Named One of America's Climate Leaders by USA Today for Second Year in a Row
summary: On the annual celebration of Earth Day, Carrier Global Corporation (NYSE: CARR), global leader in intelligent climate and energy solutions, has once again been named as one of 'America's Climate Leaders' by USA Today. The annual list highlights U.S. companies that are making significant strides in reducing greenhouse gas emissions.

headline: 1 Volatile Stock with Impressive Fundamentals and 2 to Turn Down
summary: Volatility cuts both ways - while it creates opportunities, it also increases risk, making sharp declines just as likely as big gains. This unpredictability can shake out even the most experienced investors.
